argin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">That=E2=80=99s not to say that Target doesn=E2=
=80=99t have some beauty-related
issues of its own=E2=80=94specifically, the ongoing fallout from <strong>Bl=
ake</strong> <strong>Lively</strong>=E2=80=99s personal drama with <em>It E=
nds With Us </em>director and co-star <strong>Justin</strong> <strong>Baldo=
ni</strong>, which is apparently weighing on Target=E2=80=99s lofty ambitio=
ns for Blake Brown, the actress=E2=80=99s haircare line. (For the latest on=
 the actual legal drama, read my partner <strong>Eriq Gardner</strong>=E2=
=80=99s recent masterstroke,
<a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1lEQUt2Uktx=
clJLZ0dVU0JmUWE1Z25zd1NYVXZ1LVI1VT0iLCJocmVmIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly9wdWNrLm5ld3MvYmx=
ha2UtbGl2ZWx5LXYtanVzdGluLWJhbGRvbmktcm91bmQtMi8_dXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPUxpbmUrU2=
hlZXQrLStTVUJTQ1JJQkVSUyslMjgxJTJGOCUyRjI1JTI5XHUwMDI2dXRtX2NvbnRlbnQ9TGluZ=
StTaGVldCstK1NVQlNDUklCRVJTKyUyODElMkYyJTJGMjUlMjlcdTAwMjZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVt=
YWlsX2FjdGlvblx1MDAyNnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9Y3VzdG9tZXIuaW9cdTAwMjZ1dG1fdGVybT1mNmM=
